# i18n — `languages/french-typo.pot`

- The repo tracks **only** [`languages/french-typo.pot`](languages/french-typo.pot). Locales (e.g. `fr_FR`) are maintained on [translate.wordpress.org](https://translate.wordpress.org/), not as committed `.po`/`.mo` here.
- **Do not manually edit** the `.pot`. Regenerate with `wp i18n make-pot` (see [`docs/development.md`](docs/development.md)).
